{"tid":505753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8歲女遭問路男噴液體　整臉潰爛重傷","createTime":"2017-12-21T13:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T13:39:30.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"889d689da7c68e569b8def809a73f703ded282fc","tid":505753,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong>8歲女遭問路男噴液體　整臉潰爛重傷</strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171221/640_dfacdaaeff2df016ab530e31c1df993e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171221%2F640_dfacdaaeff2df016ab530e31c1df993e.jpg&h=a6b0f9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本和歌山縣田邊市一名8歲國小女童，前天下午回家途中，被一名下車問路的男子攻擊噴灑液體，由於事發地點人煙稀少，後來有人聽到女童哭泣聲才發現。女童傷勢嚴重整臉潰爛，復原需要3個月。<br />\n<br />\n據《朝日新聞》報導，當地警方事後從監視器畫面鎖定駛離現場的銀色車輛，並循線逮浦20歲的市府臨時員工宮下裕介，他坦承犯行。警方從他的供詞研判，噴出的液體可能是催淚瓦斯。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171221/1263959/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263959%2F&d=bVtLeELf695KmgS203iLZSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6ecae631\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263959%2F&h=4928b545\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171221/1263959/</a>"},{"pid":"bcca34e41d286a6dc5c40430c7d4eb05b199a894","tid":505753,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cccb7a732cfec2824742dc083ce27c2934c4789c","tid":505753,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7946f2d9577b816e0dd719c94cba537db3a270a","tid":505753,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"日本成日有呢啲極端痴線佬"},